#ADVISORY | 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩’𝙨 𝙘𝙤𝙤𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙜… 𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙮 𝙩𝙪𝙣𝙚𝙙! 🍳✨

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟

#ABCGoldenIsabela
#ISABCG

Caption by Libradette Aranas

message.text:
#ADVISORY | 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩’𝙨 𝙘𝙤𝙤𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙜… 𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙮 𝙩𝙪𝙣𝙚𝙙! 🍳✨

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟

#ABCGoldenIsabela
#ISABCG

Caption by Libradette Aranas

#ADVISORY | 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩’𝙨 𝙘𝙤𝙤𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙜… 𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙮 𝙩𝙪𝙣𝙚𝙙! 🍳✨

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟

#ABCGoldenIsabela
#ISABCG

Caption by Libradette Aranas

#ADVISORY | 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩’𝙨 𝙘𝙤𝙤𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙜… 𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙮 𝙩𝙪𝙣𝙚𝙙! 🍳✨

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟

#ABCGoldenIsabela
#ISABCG

message.text:
#ADVISORY | 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙚𝙭𝙘𝙞𝙩𝙚𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩’𝙨 𝙘𝙤𝙤𝙠𝙞𝙣𝙜… 𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙮 𝙩𝙪𝙣𝙚𝙙! 🍳✨

We’re putting the finishing touches on the 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗔𝗻𝘁𝗶-𝗕𝘂𝗹𝗹𝘆𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗖𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗚𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗽 𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗰𝘂𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗶𝘁𝘁𝗲𝗲 acceptance emails to make sure every application gets the attention it deserves.

Think of it as letting the flavors meld before the big reveal, 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗰𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗲𝗮𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗶𝘀 𝗮𝗹𝗺𝗼𝘀𝘁 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲! While you wait, keep that energy going, because we can’t wait to see all the amazing things you’ll bring to the group.

The acceptance emails have now been rescheduled to 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟭𝟵, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱. The countdown might have a tiny pause, but the impact you’ll make starts from day one! 🌟

#ABCGoldenIsabela
#ISABCG

Caption by Libradette Aranas

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
